@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About | Selianord MCT</PageTitle>

<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="section-tag">About</p>
        <h1>About Lusukama Selemani</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
            Microsoft Certified Trainer, software developer, and learning solutions specialist
            focused on practical technology education, curriculum support, and digital transformation.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container about-profile-grid">

        <div class="about-image-card">
            <img src="images/selemani-mct.png" alt="Lusukama Selemani Microsoft Certified Trainer" class="about-profile-image" />
        </div>

        <div class="about-intro-card">
            <h2>Professional Profile</h2>
            <p>
                Lusukama Selemani is a Microsoft Certified Trainer with experience in Microsoft technologies,
                software development, cloud-focused solutions, technical education, and curriculum support.
            </p>
            <p>
                He works with individuals, institutions, and organisations to deliver practical training,
                digital solutions, and high-quality learning content aligned with modern industry needs.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-badges">
                <span class="badge">MCT Certified</span>
                <span class="badge">Azure Instructor</span>
                <span class="badge">Software Developer</span>
                <span class="badge">Curriculum Specialist</span>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-soft">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-tag">Core Strengths</p>
            <h2>What I Bring</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="about-strength-grid">
            <div class="about-card">
                <h3>Microsoft Certification Training</h3>
                <p>
                    Instructor-led training aligned with certification pathways and practical implementation skills.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
                <h3>Azure and Cloud Solutions</h3>
                <p>
                    Experience in cloud-focused teaching, solution support, and Microsoft technology ecosystems.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
                <h3>Software Development</h3>
                <p>
                    Web development, business systems, APIs, and digital solutions using modern Microsoft tools.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
                <h3>Learning Content Development</h3>
                <p>
                    Development of learner guides, assessments, presentations, and curriculum-aligned resources.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container about-highlights-grid">

        <div class="about-card">
            <p class="section-tag">Professional Highlights</p>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Microsoft Certified Trainer</li>
                <li>Trainer in cloud, development, and digital skills</li>
                <li>Experience in academic and corporate learning delivery</li>
                <li>Technical curriculum and assessment support</li>
                <li>Focus on practical, industry-relevant education</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <p class="section-tag">Mission</p>
            <h3>Empowering growth through practical technology training</h3>
            <p>
                My mission is to equip learners, teams, and institutions with practical digital skills,
                structured learning support, and technology solutions that create real value.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <p class="section-tag">Vision</p>
            <h3>Building future-ready learners and organisations</h3>
            <p>
                My vision is to contribute to a stronger technology learning ecosystem through Microsoft training,
                software development, and modern educational support services.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to work with a Microsoft Certified Trainer?</h2>
        <p>
            Let’s discuss training, learning content support, or digital solution opportunities.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
</section>